data.description: Beautiful, sharp contemporary. Open spacious floorplan with large loft, balcony & courtyard in a gated community with awesome amenities. Low Hoa fee INCLUDES Cable and internet! Cable has 3 boxes and 220 channels w HBO & Showtime. Primary bedroom separate from downstairs bedroom & bath allows privacy, Granite countertops in kitchen with stainless appliances, backsplash, breakfast bar overlooking the large great room with balcony. W/D & refrigerator & microwave included. 1 car garage. Ring Doorbell, Smart Programmable Thermostat, and Front Door Keypad. Great amenities include Gated entry, 3 Pools + a separate Tot pool, Splash Pads, Basketball Court, Dog Park, Kid's Park, and BBQ Areas. Located close to shopping, dining, casino, expressway & short drive to Nellis AFB. BUILDER JUST SOLD THIS MODEL AT $332,990. Move into lots of equity. ASK about how we can get you buy down rate or closing costs.
